Package ca.queensu.cs.cisc124.notes.interfaces

Class Range

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.queensu.cs.cisc124.notes.interfaces.Range
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Integer>
    public class Range
extends Object
implements Iterable<Integer>
    An immutable sequence of integer values having a starting and stopping value. The stopping value is not considered part of the range. An empty range has the same start and stop values.
